{"tid":1386484,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警世文，721事件背後原因（新界癌）","createTime":"2019-07-30T10:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:29:06.000Z","uid":94051,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"81d35904127400579809ecd259b827242ddfe3ec","tid":1386484,"uid":94051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:57:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w2dHKTSP5r0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw2dHKTSP5r0&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCudHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=9f233e29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w2dHKTSP5r0</a><br />\n<br />\n後半部完全解釋曬元朗官鄕黑係英治時代同港共時代既分別，新界癌係依個政府已經冇人可以解決到，背後利益太大，莊閒已經唔由政府話時，導致7 21元朗既事件<br />\n左派治新界西已成事實，中共式管治（城管，黑社會，武警），最終導致721元朗事件，官商黑勾結放曬係台面比香港巿民係721度睇得一清二楚<br />\n趕時間可以由1:07:00開始睇<br />\n<br />\n睇完明白朱凱迪其實係幾咁冇助，自己人生安全都保障唔到係唔係講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我地一定要堅持五大訴求，光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7671cdfe06d0d55ab94097c154eb04819cfc4046","tid":1386484,"uid":167142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:58:39.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00d2965d7e65bc0171126777660e107c29ea0a4","tid":1386484,"uid":94051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:03:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43275a059af33739076552714a1cc1fac3bfa8a9","tid":1386484,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:10:54.000Z","msg":"不分化，各有各做。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4c93166fe6d2b4a65d2da2a7ef3f40f625325a42","tid":1386484,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:29:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"}]}